NOTE ON eBPF CODE:

The file `netwatch.bpf.c` is licensed under GPL v2, as required by the Linux
kernel for eBPF programs using GPL-only kernel helpers (such as bpf_perf_event_output).

This dual licensing allows:
- Userspace code (netwatch.c) to be used in any project (MIT)
- BPF code (netwatch.bpf.c) to be loaded into the Linux kernel (GPL v2)

